Package: FMIndex
Type: Package
Title: FM Index Computation for DNA Sequences
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Negin", "Kafee", email = "negin.kafee@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-2345-6789"))
Description: The FMIndex package provides functions to compute the FM Index 
    for a DNA sequence provided in a FASTA file. This includes computation of 
    the Burrows-Wheeler Transform, suffix array, occurrence table, and C table 
    for efficient sequence matching and data compression.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
biocViews: SequenceMatching, DataRepresentation
